{
  "texts": [
    "The class token is randomly initialized and can be trained, serving as the fifth input.",
    "It enables aggregate global features from all other inputs and avoids bias towards a specific time step in the sequence.",
    "However, the self-attention mechanism ignores the temporal order of the inputs.",
    "To address this issue, we incorporate positional encoding to preprocess the inputs.",
    "Both the learnable positional encoding and sine cosine coding are tested in this research."
  ]
}